    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay but it feels like u are saying the deterrence argument is just flat out wrong or fake. if the evidence is so \"consistent\" that it doesn't work, then isn't the whole \"tough on crime\" approach just a failed ideology? like, is there any actual legitimate scientific basis for it anymore, or is it just something people cling to for political reasons?",
